{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回「劫后余生」讲述陆小凤在海上风暴后幸存，抱着一尊弥勒佛木像漂流到一座荒岛。他在岛上靠青铜夜壶改造成的刀具搭建简陋居所，独自忍受了一个月的寂寞。第三十三天，他发现一处隐秘山谷，竟遇见了同样幸存的岳洋。岳洋衣着华丽、武功精进，却对陆小凤冷淡至极，反问而不答，甚至动手相逼。此时山谷主人吴明出现制止，邀陆小凤参加庆典。陆小凤在水阁中见到了自认贺知章转世的贺尚书、冷艳神秘的赌客沙曼等人，得知此地实行「自食其力」的规则。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们还没有浮上来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那小子一定是故意这么说来气我的，他又不是神仙，怎么能在三天前就已知道这条船会翻？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "下次你若再掉下海，惟一能吃到的，就是你自己的肉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "跟你同船的人都已死得干干净净，你躺在这里大笑，你这算是哪一门的菩萨？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "你对别人虽然不义，却总算救了我，我不该骂你的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "你一定也渴了，我去找点水来大家喝。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是没有船只经过，难道我就要在这荒岛上过一辈子？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "看来我们已只有在这地方呆一阵子了，我们总不能就这么样像野狗一样活下去，我们好歹也得像样子一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆小凤，陆小凤，你几时变成这样没出息的子只会像女人一样盘算这些婆婆妈妈的事，难道你真想这么样过一辈子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_mi_le_fo",
      "text": "我可不像你一样，整天躺在这里，从今天开始，我也不能整天陪着你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你怎么也会在这里的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不在这里在哪里？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "翻船的时候你到哪里去了？我怎么找不到你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "翻船的时候你到哪里去了？我怎么找不到你？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "是谁救了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是谁救了你？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这些日子来，你一直都在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这些日子来，你一直都在这里？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这些事你都不必问。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我既然已经来了，怎么能不问？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还可以从原路退回去，现在还来得及。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你就算杀了我，我也绝不会退回去的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么我就杀了你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你退回去，我不杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你杀了我，我也不退。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我早就说过，我这一辈子从来也没有后悔。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "贵客光临，你这样就不是待客之道了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "青年人的礼貌疏慢，阁下千万莫要怪罪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "没关系，我跟他本就是老朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "老友重逢，那是再好也没有的了，少时我一定摆酒为两位庆贺。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "山居寂寞，少有住客，只要有一点小事可以庆贺，我们都不会错过的，何况是这种事？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "却不知贵客尊姓大名。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "原来是陆公子，久仰得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天我们这里恰巧也有小小的庆典，却不知贵客是否愿意光临？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "今天你们庆贺的是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天是小女第一次会自己吃饭的日子，所以大家就聚起来，将那天她吃的莱饭再吃一次。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆公子心里一定好笑，连这种鸡毛蒜皮的事都要庆贺，世上值得庆贺的事也未免太多了，可告慰的是，小女自幼贪吃，所以自己第一次吃饭，就要人弄了一大桌酒菜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这里多年未有外客，今日陆公子忽然光临，看来倒是小女的运气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "等我吃光了你们的酒肉时，你们就知道这是不是运气了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "主人多礼，我若连主人的尊姓大名都未曾请教，岂非也不是做客之道？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我姓吴，叫吴明，口天吴，日月明。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实我最多只不过有张多嘴而又好吃的口而已，说到日月之明，是连一点都没有的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这里大家都漫不拘礼，陆公子也千万莫要客气才好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "既然大家都漫不拘礼，为什么要叫我陆公子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他姓贺，只要喝了点酒，就硬说自己是唐时的贺知章转生，所以大家就索性叫他贺尚书，他却喜欢自称四明狂客。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "难怪他已有了醉意，既然是饮中八仙，不醉就不对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "又输光了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你还要多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "你什么时候还给我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "下一次。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "好，用你的首饰做抵押，还给我的时候再付利息。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们这里并没有什么规矩，可是大家都能谨守一个原则。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "什么原则？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "自食其力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天你当然是客人，只要不去跟他们赌，完全用不着一文钱。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "他们在赌什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "在赌骰子，他们喜欢赌得痛快。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "我可不可以看看？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然可以。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过你若要赌，就一定要小心沙曼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "沙曼就是刚才来借钱的那个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
